description: A generative reflection of life's inherent ups and downs, of the oscillations in mood and spirit that we all endure. Just as markets surge and plummet, so do our emotions, hopes, and dreams. Volatility is a representation of the peaks of euphoria and the troughs of despair. It's personal, yet universal - a testimony to the wild ride that is life and the quest for balance in the midst of chaos. Note: Go to the official ordinals content link and press 'S' to download the high resolution PNG.
name: Volatility by Lemonhaze
